PROJECT QUOTATION

Project Title:

Dynamic CMS Admin Panel with Multi-User Login and SEO-Friendly Frontend


1. User Authentication & Multi-role Login

●    Secure login system using JWT-based authentication

●    User roles: Admin, Manager, Agent, and possibly Client

●    Role-based access control:

○    Admin: Full access

○    Manager: Moderate access (e.g., can manage users or pages)

○    Agent: Limited to chat dashboard

●    Password encryption, forgot password, and user session management


2. Dashboard Module

●    A real-time dashboard for admin to view:

○    Total number of inquiries

○    Total number of active/live service pages

○    Number of pages created

○    Number of registered users

●    Clean and responsive layout with graphical representation (optional)


3. CMS Settings

●    Dedicated section called "CMS Settings"

●    Admin can manage:

○    Home Page: Add/edit banners, content blocks, testimonials, etc.

○    Service Pages: Add new services, delete or update existing ones

●    Modular and dynamic—admin doesn't need to touch code


4. Editable Contact Us & Portfolio Page

●    Contact Page:

○    Admin can edit contact details, Google map embed, address, email, phone

○    Form submission setup for direct database and WhatsApp API

●    Portfolio Page:

○    Add projects with title, description, images, video links

○    Edit or delete portfolio entries


5. Cloud API Configuration Page

●    UI for entering and editing configuration values of 3rd-party APIs

●    Example: WhatsApp API key, Amazon Lex tokens, cloud DB URLs

●    Makes updating cloud integrations easier without code access


6. Template Management Page

●    Admin can add/edit/delete UI templates used across pages

●    Choose design templates for service listings, landing pages, etc.

●    Useful for reusing frontend layouts without hardcoding


7. User Management

●    View, add, edit, and delete platform users

●    Assign roles and permissions

●    Reset user passwords or deactivate users

●    Export user list in Excel/CSV


8. Cloud API Chat Dashboard

●    Central dashboard to manage incoming chat inquiries via Cloud API

●    Assign chat requests to specific agents

●    Agents will have their own panel to respond

●    Chat history and timestamps maintained

●    Can integrate with Amazon Lex chatbot for auto-responses


9. SEO-Friendly URL Architecture

●    Page URLs will follow slugs like:

 /services/website-development instead of /page?id=123

●    Optimized for search engines (Google, Bing)

●    Meta title, description, and OG tags editable per page


10. Multi-language Support

●    Internationalization (i18n) setup for frontend

●    Users can switch between languages (e.g., English, Hindi, Arabic)

●    Dynamic content translation support

●    Language toggler in the navbar


11. Frontend Development using Next.js + Tailwind CSS 4

●    Modern, fast, and SEO-optimized frontend using:

○    Next.js: For server-side rendering, speed, and routing

○    Tailwind 4: Latest utility-first CSS framework

●    Fully mobile responsive

●    Structured for future scalability


12. Amazon Lex Chatbot Integration

●    AI-powered chatbot integrated on website

●    Amazon Lex handles customer queries and gives pre-trained answers

●    Can pass complex queries to human agents

●    Custom workflows like booking appointments or capturing inquiry forms

13. WhatsApp API Integration

●    When a user submits an inquiry form:

○    Admin/agent instantly gets a WhatsApp notification

●    Fast response time, better engagement


14. Testing, Optimization & Deployment

●    Full testing of all modules

●    Bug fixing, UI responsiveness check

●    SEO audit and page load optimization

●    Deployment to live server (AWS, Vercel, or custom hosting)
